<br />
<br />I may have to find the time to learn more about media wiki. If we could add an approval process for images and the image (or supposed to be image) cannot be accessed by anyone, then in that case that remove the possibility of using the wiki as a hiding place for files.
<br />
<br />You may say that I may be too drastic but we have the responsibility to make the wiki safe.  And since the hosting is free, we have to be even more careful to not abuse Koitsu's good will.

		

